# 🎯 AI Interview Coach

An AI-powered mock interview platform that helps students practice role-specific interview questions with instant feedback and personalized improvement suggestions.

## ✨ Features

- **Role-Specific Questions**: Practice for Python Developer, Data Scientist, Web Developer, and more
- **Difficulty Levels**: Beginner, Intermediate, Advanced to match your experience
- **Instant Feedback**: Get scores and constructive feedback on every answer
- **Improved Answers**: See how to structure better responses
- **Session Summary**: Receive comprehensive analysis of strengths and areas to improve
- **Zero Cost**: Free to use with Gemini API

## 🚀 Quick Start

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.8+
- Gemini API Key (free from makersuite.google.com/app/apikey)

### Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/ai-interview-coach.git
cd ai-interview-coach

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Set up API key
echo "GEMINI_API_KEY=your_api_key_here" > .env

# Run the app
streamlit run app.py